<HL>
   Who's News:
   Philip Morris Picks
   Viault to Be Chief
   Of Jacobs Suchard
   ----
   By Kathleen Deveny
   Staff Reporter of The Wall Street Journal
</HL>
<DATE>
08/17/90
</DATE>
<SO>
WALL STREET JOURNAL (J), PAGE C8
</SO>
